          "vlandia"
        ],
        "KingdomIds": null,
        "SettlementIds": null,
        "Roles": null,
        "IdentityIds": null,
        "IsFemale": null,
        "IsClanLeader": null,
        "SkillMin": null
      },
      "Content": "鲁兰德的猪是在橡树林里放养的，吃橡子长大的猪肉有一股特别的香味。帕拉汶德那边王宫里办宴会，烤乳猪有不少就是从鲁兰德运过去的。"
    },
    {
      "Priority": 0,
      "When": {
        "HeroIds": null,
        "Cultures": [
          "vlandia"
        ],
        "KingdomIds": null,
        "SettlementIds": null,
        "Roles": [
          "merchant",
          "townsfolk"
        ],
        "IdentityIds": null,
        "IsFemale": null,
        "IsClanLeader": null,
        "SkillMin": null
      },
      "Content": "鲁兰德的熏肉在帕拉汶德的市场上很受欢迎。林谷里的橡树秋天落一地橡子，猪吃得膘肥体壮，肉又紧又香。价比别处稍贵一点，但值。"
    },
    {
      "Priority": 0,
      "When": {
        "HeroIds": null,
        "Cultures": null,
        "KingdomIds": null,
        "SettlementIds": null,
        "Roles": [
          "wanderer"
        ],
        "IdentityIds": null,
        "IsFemale": null,
        "IsClanLeader": null,
        "SkillMin": null
      },
      "Content": "我在鲁兰德歇过脚，那地方在林谷里，安静得很，到处是橡树。秋天的时候，林子地上铺满了橡子，猪在上面拱来拱去，吃得比人还自在。"
    }
  ],
